EMAIL REFERRAL PROGRAM
We work with a trusted third party partner, Firewards, to provide subscribers to our marketing emails with the option to participate in our email referral program. Your personal data, including your name and email address, may be shared with Firewards in order to provide this service. The email referral program is an optional service for our users and if you do not wish to participate, do not follow the opt in instructions set out in the email. If you opt out of receiving emails from Oddschecker, you will also automatically be opted out of the Firewards program.
For more information on the privacy practices of Firewards, please visit the Firewards Privacy Policy page: https://www.firewards.com/company/privacy-policy
